  "page": 41,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0002",
      "text": " 22",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0003",
      "text": "An Nx_Port receiving an ELS request shall respond to it in accord with table 4, depending on its",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.58,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0004",
      "text": "N_Port Login state with the Nx_Port sending the ELS request and the PLOGI requirement for the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.93,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0005",
      "text": "ELS specified in table 3.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        203.25,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0006",
      "text": "An Nx_Port is not required to generate and send the PLOGI ELS request. However, if an Nx_Port re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        540.09,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0007",
      "text": "ceives a PLOGI ELS request, the Nx_Port shall respond with a LS_ACC Link Service Reply, or with",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        540.05,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0008",
      "text": "LS_RJT. LS_RJT shall not be issued with a reason code of \"Command not supported\" in response to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        539.97,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0009",
      "text": "a PLOGI.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        137.65,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0010",
      "text": "NOTE 1 – If an Nx_Port that does not generate PLOGI, is in a point-to-point topology, and has an",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        395.18,
        539.99,
        405.22
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0011",
      "text": "N_Port_Name greater than the other Nx_Port's, the other Nx_Port may timeout, waiting to receive PLOGI.",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        406.22,
        525.8,
        416.26
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0012",
      "text": "There is one ELS request Sequence in which a collision is possible with the other Nx_Port involved in",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.97,
        539.96,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0013",
      "text": "the same target Exchange. This request is Request Sequence Initiative (RSI) (e.g., Nx_Port (A) may",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.97,
        539.99,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0014",
      "text": "transmit an RSI request to Nx_Port (B) at the same time that Nx_Port (B) transmits an RSI request to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.97,
        540.03,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0015",
      "text": "Nx_Port (A) for the same target Exchange).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.97,
        288.29,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0016",
      "text": "If such an instance occurs, the Originator Nx_Port of the target Exchange shall reject the RSI request",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.97,
        540.08,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0017",
      "text": "sequence with an LS_RJT with a reason code of \"command already in progress\". The Responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.97,
        539.9,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0018",
      "text": "Nx_Port of the target Exchange shall honor and process the RSI request Sequence normally.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        507.72,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0019",
      "text": "4.2.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        118.22,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0020",
      "text": "Sequence and Exchange management",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        538.96,
        310.37,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0021",
      "text": "Extended Link Service communication shall observe all relevant rules of FC-FS-2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        457.54,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0022",
      "text": "All ELS requests, excluding ESTS, ESTC, and ADVC, and the corresponding replies shall be per-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.03,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0023",
      "text": "formed within a single Exchange, intended exclusively for the purpose of ELS processing (see FC-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.07,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0024",
      "text": "FS-2 for the procedure using ESTS, ESTC, and ADVC). The Advise Credit request may also be per-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        540.16,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0025",
      "text": "formed in a separate Exchange. Most ELS protocols are performed as a two Sequence Exchange.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        540.0,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0026",
      "text": "Each of these two Sequence Exchanges consist of a request Sequence by the Originator, transfer of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        540.06,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0027",
      "text": "Sequence Initiative, and a reply Sequence from the Responder that terminates the Exchange by set-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.09,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0028",
      "text": "ting the Last_Sequence bit (bit 20) in F_CTL.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        294.82,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0029",
      "text": "More than one frame may be used to form a request or reply Sequence.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        413.75,
        694.14
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0030",
      "text": " Table 4 – Responses to Received ELSs",
      "bbox": [
        223.86,
        103.66,
        412.17,
        114.78
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0031",
      "text": "N_Port Login ",
      "bbox": [
        110.22,
        125.62,
        175.73,
        136.74
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0032",
      "text": "Required? (see ",
      "bbox": [
        105.48,
        137.62,
        180.51,
        148.74
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0033",
      "text": "table 3)",
      "bbox": [
        124.08,
        149.62,
        159.1,
        160.74
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0034",
      "text": "Logged in with Source N_Port?",
      "bbox": [
        289.44,
        125.62,
        438.24,
        136.74
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0035",
      "text": "Yes",
      "bbox": [
        266.76,
        149.62,
        284.54,
        160.74
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0036",
      "text": "No",
      "bbox": [
        445.38,
        149.62,
        458.72,
        160.74
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0037",
      "text": "Yes",
      "bbox": [
        132.96,
        168.64,
        150.18,
        179.76
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0038",
      "text": "Respond as appropriate for the ELS ",
      "bbox": [
        189.48,
        214.66,
        351.66,
        225.78
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0039",
      "text": "and the current state of the Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        189.48,
        226.66,
        347.77,
        237.78
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0040",
      "text": "If a reply sequence is defined for the ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        166.66,
        529.75,
        177.78
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0041",
      "text": "ELS, originate a LOGO ELS Exchange ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        178.66,
        539.4,
        189.78
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0042",
      "text": "to the sender of the received ELS or ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        190.66,
        528.61,
        201.78
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0043",
      "text": "reply with an LS_RJT ELS Sequence ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        202.66,
        533.02,
        213.78
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0044",
      "text": "with a reason code of \"Unable to ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        214.66,
        512.8,
        225.78
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0045",
      "text": "perform command request\" and a ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        226.66,
        517.13,
        237.78
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0046",
      "text": "reason code explanation of \"N_Port ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        238.66,
        526.09,
        249.77
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0047",
      "text": "Login required\".",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        250.66,
        436.05,
        261.77
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0048",
      "text": "If a reply sequence is not defined for the ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        262.66,
        540.1,
        273.77
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0049",
      "text": "ELS, it shall be discarded",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        274.66,
        478.65,
        285.77
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 10,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0050",
      "text": "No",
      "bbox": [
        135.18,
        293.62,
        147.98,
        304.73
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0051",
      "text": "Respond as appropriate for the ELS ",
      "bbox": [
        189.48,
        291.64,
        351.66,
        302.75
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0052",
      "text": "and the current state of the Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        189.48,
        303.64,
        350.62,
        314.75
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0053",
      "text": "Respond as appropriate for the ELS ",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        291.64,
        528.05,
        302.75
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p041_s0054",
      "text": "and the current state of the Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        365.88,
        303.64,
        527.01,
        314.75
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
